{
  "stem": "20021.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I would take that trip in that truck, and sit in the cabin with two drivers, you see, in-- in between them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One would be driving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would be sitting in the middle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next one would sit at the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And either I fell asleep and mumbled something, or they by close observation over such a long trip, somehow they suspected that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they tipped off their friends, who came one day, and acted as policemen, and entered the house, and flashed a-- you know, document.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We are from the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And started to interrogate me, and then they say, come with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'm going with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here's my suitcase which I took.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the suitcase had lots of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they saw that the suitcase had lots of money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we go and go, and I kind of wonder to myself, shall I run, or shall I not run?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shall I run?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I run, they'll catch me and all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as we keep coming closer and closer, suddenly they kind of suggest to me that if I run for my life or something like that, they might not do anything, just because I'm a nice person.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In short, I recognize that they were not real policemen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were just blackmailing me, because, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this later I found out from many friends was-- was the common procedure that many people suddenly engaged in catching Jews who are hiding as I did, and blackmailing them, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what choice did I have?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, now, I didn't want to give them my suitcase with the money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they tried to make me run for my life and leave the suitcase with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
